{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"For a moment, what I need to do"},{"time":3000,"text":"is project something on the screen of your imagination."},{"time":8000,"text":"We're in 17th century Japan"},{"time":10000,"text":"on the west coast,"},{"time":13000,"text":"and a little, wizened monk"},{"time":16000,"text":"is hurrying along, near midnight,"},{"time":19000,"text":"to the crest of a small hill."},{"time":22000,"text":"He arrives on the small hill,"},{"time":24000,"text":"dripping with water."},{"time":26000,"text":"He stands there,"},{"time":28000,"text":"and he looks across at the island, Sado."},{"time":31000,"text":"And he scans across the ocean, and he looks at the sky."},{"time":36000,"text":"Then he says to himself, very quietly,"},{"time":40000,"text":"\"[Turbulent the sea,]"},{"time":43000,"text":"[Stretching across to Sado]"},{"time":46000,"text":"[The Milky Way].\""},{"time":49000,"text":"Basho was a brilliant man."},{"time":53000,"text":"He said more with less"},{"time":55000,"text":"than any human"},{"time":57000,"text":"that I have ever read or talked to."},{"time":61000,"text":"Basho, in 17 syllables,"},{"time":64000,"text":"juxtaposed"},{"time":67000,"text":"a turbulent ocean"},{"time":69000,"text":"driven by a storm now past,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and captured the almost"},{"time":76000,"text":"impossible beauty"},{"time":79000,"text":"of our home galaxy"},{"time":82000,"text":"with millions of stars,"},{"time":86000,"text":"probably hundreds and hundreds of -- who knows how many -- planets,"},{"time":89000,"text":"maybe even an ocean"},{"time":91000,"text":"that we will probably call Sylvia in time."},{"time":97000,"text":"As he was nearing his death,"},{"time":100000,"text":"his disciples and followers"},{"time":103000,"text":"kept asking him,"},{"time":105000,"text":"\"What's the secret?"},{"time":107000,"text":"How can you"},{"time":109000,"text":"make haiku poems so beautiful so easily?\""},{"time":114000,"text":"And toward the end, he said,"},{"time":119000,"text":"\"If you would know the pine tree,"},{"time":122000,"text":"go to the pine tree.\""},{"time":125000,"text":"That was it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"Sylvia has said we must use"},{"time":132000,"text":"every capacity we have"},{"time":135000,"text":"in order to know the oceans."},{"time":137000,"text":"If we would know the oceans,"},{"time":139000,"text":"we must go to the oceans."},{"time":141000,"text":"And what I'd like to talk to you today about, a little bit,"},{"time":144000,"text":"is really transforming"},{"time":147000,"text":"the relationship, or the interplay,"},{"time":150000,"text":"between humans and oceans"},{"time":152000,"text":"with a new capability"},{"time":155000,"text":"that is not at all routine yet."},{"time":157000,"text":"I hope it will be."},{"time":160000,"text":"There are a few key points."},{"time":162000,"text":"One of them is the oceans are central"},{"time":164000,"text":"to the quality of life on earth."},{"time":168000,"text":"Another is that there are bold, new ways"},{"time":171000,"text":"of studying oceans"},{"time":173000,"text":"that we have not used well yet."},{"time":176000,"text":"And the last is that these bold, new ways"},{"time":178000,"text":"that we are exploring"},{"time":180000,"text":"as a community"},{"time":182000,"text":"will transform the way we look at our planet, our oceans,"},{"time":185000,"text":"and eventually how we manage"},{"time":187000,"text":"probably the entire planet, for what it's worth."},{"time":192000,"text":"So what scientists do when they begin"},{"time":194000,"text":"is to start with the system."},{"time":196000,"text":"They define what the system is."},{"time":198000,"text":"The system isn't Chesapeake Bay."},{"time":200000,"text":"It's not the Kuril arc. It's not even the entire Pacific."},{"time":203000,"text":"It's the whole planet,"},{"time":205000,"text":"the entire planet, continents and oceans together."},{"time":208000,"text":"That's the system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"And basically, our challenge"},{"time":212000,"text":"is to optimize the benefits"},{"time":215000,"text":"and mitigate the risks"},{"time":217000,"text":"of living on a planet that's driven by only two processes,"},{"time":220000,"text":"two sources of energy,"},{"time":222000,"text":"one of which is solar,"},{"time":224000,"text":"that drives the winds, the waves,"},{"time":226000,"text":"the clouds, the storms and photosynthesis."},{"time":229000,"text":"The second one is internal energy."},{"time":231000,"text":"And these two war against one another"},{"time":233000,"text":"almost continuously."},{"time":235000,"text":"Mountain ranges, plate tectonics,"},{"time":237000,"text":"moves the continents around, forms ore deposits."},{"time":240000,"text":"Volcanoes erupt."},{"time":242000,"text":"That's the planet that we live on."},{"time":244000,"text":"It's immensely complex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"Now I don't expect all of you to see all the details here,"},{"time":248000,"text":"but what I want you to see is"},{"time":250000,"text":"this is about 10 percent"},{"time":253000,"text":"of the processes that operate within"},{"time":255000,"text":"the oceans almost continuously,"},{"time":257000,"text":"and have for the last 4 billion years."},{"time":260000,"text":"This is a system that's been around a very long time."},{"time":263000,"text":"And these have all co-evolved."},{"time":265000,"text":"What do I mean by that?"},{"time":267000,"text":"They interact with one another constantly."},{"time":270000,"text":"All of them interact with one another."},{"time":273000,"text":"So the complexity of this system that we're looking at,"},{"time":276000,"text":"the one driven by the sun --"},{"time":278000,"text":"upper portion, mostly --"},{"time":280000,"text":"and the lower portion is partly driven"},{"time":282000,"text":"by the input from heat below"},{"time":284000,"text":"and by other processes."},{"time":286000,"text":"This is very, very important"},{"time":288000,"text":"because this is the system, this is the crucible,"},{"time":290000,"text":"out of which life on the planet came,"},{"time":293000,"text":"and it's now time for us to understand it."},{"time":296000,"text":"We must understand it."},{"time":299000,"text":"That's one of the themes that Sylvia reminds us about:"},{"time":301000,"text":"understand this ocean of ours,"},{"time":304000,"text":"this basic life support system,"},{"time":307000,"text":"the dominant life support system on the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311000,"text":"Look at this complexity here."},{"time":313000,"text":"This is only one variable."},{"time":315000,"text":"If you can see the complexity,"},{"time":317000,"text":"you can see how"},{"time":319000,"text":"tiny, little eddies"},{"time":322000,"text":"and large eddies and the motion --"},{"time":324000,"text":"this is just sea surface temperature,"},{"time":326000,"text":"but it's immensely complicated."},{"time":328000,"text":"Now a layer in,"},{"time":330000,"text":"the other two or three hundred processes"},{"time":332000,"text":"that are all interacting,"},{"time":334000,"text":"partly as a function of temperature, partly as a function of all the other factors,"},{"time":337000,"text":"and you've got a really complicated system."},{"time":339000,"text":"That's our challenge, is to understand,"},{"time":342000,"text":"understand this system in new and phenomenal ways."},{"time":345000,"text":"And there's an urgency to this."},{"time":348000,"text":"Part of the urgency comes from the fact"},{"time":350000,"text":"that, of order, a billion people on the planet currently"},{"time":353000,"text":"are undernourished or starving."},{"time":356000,"text":"And part of the issue"},{"time":358000,"text":"is for Cody --"},{"time":361000,"text":"who's here,"},{"time":363000,"text":"16 years old --"},{"time":365000,"text":"and I have permission to relay this number."},{"time":368000,"text":"When he, 40 years from now,"},{"time":371000,"text":"is the age of Nancy Brown,"},{"time":373000,"text":"there are going to be"},{"time":376000,"text":"another two and a half billion people on the planet."},{"time":380000,"text":"We can't solve all the problems"},{"time":383000,"text":"by looking only at the oceans,"},{"time":385000,"text":"but if we don't understand"},{"time":387000,"text":"the fundamental life support system of this planet"},{"time":389000,"text":"much more thoroughly than we do now,"},{"time":391000,"text":"then the stresses that we will face,"},{"time":393000,"text":"and that Cody will face,"},{"time":395000,"text":"and even Nancy, who's going to live till she's 98,"},{"time":398000,"text":"will have really problems coping."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"All right, let's talk about another perspective"},{"time":405000,"text":"on the importance of the oceans."},{"time":408000,"text":"Look at this diagram, which is showing"},{"time":411000,"text":"warm waters in red,"},{"time":413000,"text":"cool waters in blue,"},{"time":415000,"text":"and on the continents, what you're seeing in bright green,"},{"time":418000,"text":"is the growth of vegetation,"},{"time":420000,"text":"and in olive green, the dieback of vegetation."},{"time":422000,"text":"And in the lower left hand corner there's a clock ticking away"},{"time":425000,"text":"from 1982 to 1998"},{"time":427000,"text":"and then cycling again."},{"time":430000,"text":"What you'll see is that the rhythms"},{"time":432000,"text":"of growth, of vegetation --"},{"time":435000,"text":"a subset of which is food on the continents --"},{"time":437000,"text":"is directly tied to the rhythms"},{"time":439000,"text":"of the sea surface temperatures."},{"time":442000,"text":"The oceans control,"},{"time":444000,"text":"or at least significantly influence,"},{"time":447000,"text":"correlate with,"},{"time":449000,"text":"the growth patterns and the drought patterns"},{"time":451000,"text":"and the rain patterns on the continents."},{"time":453000,"text":"So people in Kansas, in a wheat field in Kansas,"},{"time":456000,"text":"need to understand that the oceans"},{"time":458000,"text":"are central to them as well."},{"time":460000,"text":"Another complexity: this is the age of the oceans."},{"time":463000,"text":"I'm going to layer in on top of this"},{"time":465000,"text":"the tectonic plates."},{"time":468000,"text":"The age of the ocean, the tectonic plates,"},{"time":471000,"text":"gives rise to a totally new phenomenon"},{"time":473000,"text":"that we have heard about"},{"time":475000,"text":"in this conference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"And I share with you some very high-definition video"},{"time":480000,"text":"that we collected in real time."},{"time":483000,"text":"Seconds after this video was taken,"},{"time":486000,"text":"people in Beijing,"},{"time":488000,"text":"people in Sydney, people in Amsterdam,"},{"time":490000,"text":"people in Washington D.C. were watching this."},{"time":493000,"text":"Now you've heard of hydrothermal vents,"},{"time":495000,"text":"but the other discovery"},{"time":497000,"text":"is that deep below the sea floor,"},{"time":500000,"text":"there is vast reservoir of microbial activity,"},{"time":503000,"text":"which we have only just discovered"},{"time":505000,"text":"and we have almost no way to study."},{"time":508000,"text":"Some people have estimated"},{"time":510000,"text":"that the biomass"},{"time":512000,"text":"tied up in these microbes"},{"time":514000,"text":"living in the pours and the cracks"},{"time":516000,"text":"of the sea floor and below"},{"time":519000,"text":"rival the total amount of living biomass"},{"time":521000,"text":"at the surface of the planet."},{"time":523000,"text":"It's an astonishing insight,"},{"time":525000,"text":"and we have only found out about this recently."},{"time":527000,"text":"This is very, very exciting."},{"time":530000,"text":"It may be the next rainforest,"},{"time":533000,"text":"in terms of pharmaceuticals."},{"time":535000,"text":"We know little or nothing about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539000,"text":"Well, Marcel Proust has this wonderful saying"},{"time":542000,"text":"that, \"The real voyage of discovery"},{"time":544000,"text":"consists not so much in seeking new territory,"},{"time":547000,"text":"but possibly in having new sets of eyes,\""},{"time":550000,"text":"new ways of seeing things,"},{"time":552000,"text":"a new mindset."},{"time":554000,"text":"And many of you remember"},{"time":556000,"text":"the early stages of oceanography,"},{"time":558000,"text":"when we had to use what we had at our fingertips."},{"time":561000,"text":"And it wasn't easy. It wasn't easy in those days."},{"time":564000,"text":"Some of you remember this, I'm sure."},{"time":569000,"text":"And now, we have an entire suite of tools"},{"time":572000,"text":"that are really pretty powerful --"},{"time":574000,"text":"ships, satellites, moorings."},{"time":578000,"text":"But they don't quite cut it. They don't quite give us what we need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"And the program that I wanted to talk to you about"},{"time":583000,"text":"just a little bit here,"},{"time":585000,"text":"was funded, and it involves autonomous vehicles"},{"time":588000,"text":"like the one running across the base of this image."},{"time":591000,"text":"Modeling: on the right hand side,"},{"time":594000,"text":"there's a very complex computational model."},{"time":597000,"text":"On the left hand side, there's a new type of mooring,"},{"time":599000,"text":"which I'll show you in just a second."},{"time":601000,"text":"And on the basis"},{"time":603000,"text":"of several points,"},{"time":605000,"text":"the oceans are complex, and they're central to the life on earth."},{"time":608000,"text":"They are changing rapidly, but not predictably."},{"time":611000,"text":"And the models that we need to predict the future"},{"time":613000,"text":"do not have enough data to refine them."},{"time":615000,"text":"The computational power"},{"time":617000,"text":"is amazing."},{"time":619000,"text":"But without data, those models"},{"time":621000,"text":"will never ever be predicted."},{"time":623000,"text":"And that's what we really need."},{"time":625000,"text":"For a variety of reasons they're dangerous,"},{"time":627000,"text":"but we feel that OOI,"},{"time":629000,"text":"this Ocean Observatory Initiative,"},{"time":631000,"text":"which the National Science Foundation"},{"time":633000,"text":"has begun to fund,"},{"time":635000,"text":"has the potential to really transform things."},{"time":637000,"text":"And the goal of the program is to"},{"time":639000,"text":"launch an era of scientific discovery"},{"time":641000,"text":"and understanding"},{"time":643000,"text":"across and within the ocean basins,"},{"time":645000,"text":"utilizing widely accessible,"},{"time":648000,"text":"interactive telepresence."},{"time":651000,"text":"It's a new world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653000,"text":"We will be present throughout"},{"time":655000,"text":"the volume of the ocean, at will,"},{"time":658000,"text":"communicating in real time."},{"time":660000,"text":"And this is what the system involves,"},{"time":662000,"text":"a number of sites in the southern hemisphere,"},{"time":665000,"text":"shown in those circles."},{"time":667000,"text":"And in the northern hemisphere there are four sites."},{"time":669000,"text":"I won't talk a lot about most of them right here,"},{"time":672000,"text":"but the one on the west coast, that's in the box,"},{"time":674000,"text":"is called the regional scale nodes."},{"time":677000,"text":"It was once called Neptune."},{"time":679000,"text":"And let me show you what's behind it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682000,"text":"Fiber: next-generation way of communicating."},{"time":685000,"text":"You can see the copper tips on these things."},{"time":688000,"text":"You can transmit power,"},{"time":690000,"text":"but the bandwidth is in those tiny, little threads"},{"time":693000,"text":"smaller than the hair on your head in diameter."},{"time":696000,"text":"And this particular set here"},{"time":699000,"text":"can transmit something of the order of"},{"time":701000,"text":"three to five terabits per second."},{"time":704000,"text":"This is phenomenal bandwidth."},{"time":706000,"text":"And this is what the planet looks like."},{"time":708000,"text":"We are already laced up"},{"time":710000,"text":"as if we're in a fiber optic corset, if you like."},{"time":713000,"text":"This is what it looks like."},{"time":715000,"text":"And the cables go really continent to continent."},{"time":718000,"text":"It's a very powerful system,"},{"time":720000,"text":"and most of our communications consist of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":722000,"text":"So this is the system that I'm talking about,"},{"time":724000,"text":"off the west coast. It's coincident with the tectonic plate,"},{"time":727000,"text":"the Juan de Fuca tectonic plate."},{"time":729000,"text":"And it's going to deliver abundant power"},{"time":731000,"text":"and unprecedented bandwidth"},{"time":733000,"text":"across this entire volume --"},{"time":735000,"text":"in the overlying ocean,"},{"time":737000,"text":"on the sea floor and below the sea floor."},{"time":739000,"text":"Bandwidth and power"},{"time":741000,"text":"and a wide variety of processes"},{"time":743000,"text":"that will be operating."},{"time":745000,"text":"This is what one of those primary nodes looks like,"},{"time":747000,"text":"and it's like a sub station with power and bandwidth"},{"time":750000,"text":"that can spread out over an area the size of Seattle."},{"time":754000,"text":"And the kind of science that can be done"},{"time":756000,"text":"will be determined by a variety of scientists who want to be involved"},{"time":759000,"text":"and can bring the instrumentation to the table."},{"time":762000,"text":"They will bring it and link it in."},{"time":764000,"text":"It'll be, in a sense, like having time on a telescope,"},{"time":767000,"text":"except you'll have your own port."},{"time":770000,"text":"Climate change, ocean acidification,"},{"time":772000,"text":"dissolved oxygen,"},{"time":774000,"text":"carbon cycle, coastal upwelling,"},{"time":776000,"text":"fishing dynamics --"},{"time":778000,"text":"the full spectrum of"},{"time":780000,"text":"earth science and ocean science"},{"time":782000,"text":"simultaneously in the same volume."},{"time":784000,"text":"So anyone coming along later"},{"time":786000,"text":"simply accesses the database"},{"time":789000,"text":"and can draw down the information they need"},{"time":791000,"text":"about anything that has taken place."},{"time":793000,"text":"And this is just the first of these."},{"time":796000,"text":"In conjunction with our Canadian colleagues, we've set this up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"Now I want to take you into the caldera."},{"time":801000,"text":"On the left hand side there"},{"time":803000,"text":"is a large volcano called Axial Seamount."},{"time":806000,"text":"And we're going to go down into the Axial Seamount"},{"time":808000,"text":"using animation."},{"time":810000,"text":"Here's what this system is going to look like"},{"time":812000,"text":"that we are funded to build at this point."},{"time":815000,"text":"Very powerful."},{"time":817000,"text":"That's an elevator that's constantly moving up and down,"},{"time":819000,"text":"but it can be controlled by the folks on land"},{"time":822000,"text":"who are responsible for it."},{"time":824000,"text":"Or they can transfer control"},{"time":826000,"text":"to someone in India or China"},{"time":828000,"text":"who can take over for a while,"},{"time":830000,"text":"because it's all going to be directly connected"},{"time":832000,"text":"through the Internet."},{"time":834000,"text":"There will be massive amounts of data flowing ashore,"},{"time":837000,"text":"all available to anyone who has any interest in using it."},{"time":840000,"text":"This is going to be much more powerful"},{"time":842000,"text":"than having a single ship"},{"time":844000,"text":"in a single location,"},{"time":846000,"text":"then move to a new location."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"We're flying across the caldera floor."},{"time":852000,"text":"There is a number of robotic systems."},{"time":854000,"text":"There's cameras that can be turned on and off at your will,"},{"time":857000,"text":"if those are your experiments."},{"time":859000,"text":"The kinds of systems that will be down there,"},{"time":861000,"text":"the kinds of instruments that will be on the sea floor,"},{"time":864000,"text":"consist of -- if you can read them there --"},{"time":866000,"text":"there's cameras, there's pressure sensors,"},{"time":868000,"text":"fluorometers, there's seismometers."},{"time":870000,"text":"It's a full spectrum of tools."},{"time":872000,"text":"Now, that mound right there"},{"time":874000,"text":"actually looks like this."},{"time":876000,"text":"This is what it actually looks like."},{"time":879000,"text":"And this is the kind of activity"},{"time":881000,"text":"that we can see with high-definition video,"},{"time":883000,"text":"because the bandwidth of these cables"},{"time":886000,"text":"is so huge"},{"time":888000,"text":"that we could have five to 10"},{"time":890000,"text":"stereo HD systems"},{"time":892000,"text":"running continuously"},{"time":894000,"text":"and, again, directed through robotic techniques from land."},{"time":899000,"text":"Very, very powerful."},{"time":902000,"text":"And these are the things that we're funded to do today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":904000,"text":"So what can we actually do tomorrow?"},{"time":906000,"text":"We're about to ride the wave"},{"time":908000,"text":"of technological opportunity."},{"time":911000,"text":"There are emerging technologies throughout"},{"time":914000,"text":"the field around oceanography,"},{"time":916000,"text":"which we will incorporate into oceanography,"},{"time":918000,"text":"and through that convergence,"},{"time":920000,"text":"we will transform oceanography into something even more magical."},{"time":924000,"text":"Robotics systems are just incredible these days,"},{"time":927000,"text":"absolutely incredible."},{"time":929000,"text":"And we will be bringing robotics of all sorts"},{"time":931000,"text":"into the ocean."},{"time":934000,"text":"Nanotechnology: this is a small generator."},{"time":936000,"text":"It's smaller than a postage stamp,"},{"time":938000,"text":"and it can generate power just by being"},{"time":940000,"text":"attached to your shirt as you move."},{"time":942000,"text":"Just as you move, it generates power."},{"time":945000,"text":"There are many kinds of things that can be used in the ocean, continuously."},{"time":950000,"text":"Imaging: Many of you know a good deal more about this type of thing than I,"},{"time":953000,"text":"but stereo imaging at four times the definition"},{"time":956000,"text":"that we have in HD"},{"time":958000,"text":"will be routine within five years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960000,"text":"And this is the magic one."},{"time":962000,"text":"As a result of the human genome process,"},{"time":964000,"text":"we are in a situation where"},{"time":966000,"text":"events that take place in the ocean --"},{"time":969000,"text":"like an erupting volcano, or something of that sort --"},{"time":971000,"text":"can actually be sampled."},{"time":973000,"text":"We pump the fluid through one of these systems,"},{"time":976000,"text":"and we press the button,"},{"time":978000,"text":"and it's analyzed for the genomic character."},{"time":980000,"text":"And that's transmitted back to land immediately."},{"time":983000,"text":"So in the volume of the ocean,"},{"time":985000,"text":"we will know, not just the physics and the chemistry,"},{"time":988000,"text":"but the base of the food chain"},{"time":990000,"text":"will be transparent to us"},{"time":992000,"text":"with data on a continuous basis."},{"time":995000,"text":"Grid computing: the power of grid computers"},{"time":997000,"text":"is going to be just amazing here."},{"time":999000,"text":"We will soon be using grid computing"},{"time":1001000,"text":"to do pretty much everything, like adjust the data"},{"time":1004000,"text":"and everything"},{"time":1006000,"text":"that goes with the data."},{"time":1008000,"text":"The power generation will come from the ocean itself."},{"time":1011000,"text":"And the next generation fiber"},{"time":1013000,"text":"will be simply magic."},{"time":1015000,"text":"It's far beyond what we currently have."},{"time":1018000,"text":"So the presence of the power"},{"time":1020000,"text":"and the bandwidth in the environment"},{"time":1022000,"text":"will allow all of these new technologies"},{"time":1024000,"text":"to converge in a manner that is just unprecedented."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027000,"text":"So within five to seven years,"},{"time":1029000,"text":"I see us having"},{"time":1031000,"text":"a capacity to be completely present"},{"time":1033000,"text":"throughout the ocean"},{"time":1035000,"text":"and have all of that connected to the Internet,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"so we can reach many, many folks."},{"time":1040000,"text":"Delivering the power and the bandwidth into the ocean"},{"time":1043000,"text":"will dramatically accelerate adaptation."},{"time":1046000,"text":"Here's an example."},{"time":1048000,"text":"When earthquakes take place, massive amounts"},{"time":1050000,"text":"of these new microbes we've never seen before"},{"time":1052000,"text":"come out of the sea floor."},{"time":1054000,"text":"We have a way of addressing that,"},{"time":1056000,"text":"a new way of addressing that."},{"time":1059000,"text":"We've determined from the earthquake activity that you're seeing here"},{"time":1062000,"text":"that the top of that volcano is erupting,"},{"time":1065000,"text":"so we deploy the troops."},{"time":1067000,"text":"What are the troops? The troops are the autonomous vehicles, of course."},{"time":1070000,"text":"And they fly into the erupting volcano."},{"time":1073000,"text":"They sample the fluids coming out of the sea floor"},{"time":1075000,"text":"during an eruption,"},{"time":1077000,"text":"which have the microbes that have never been"},{"time":1079000,"text":"to the surface of the planet before."},{"time":1081000,"text":"They eject it to the surface where it floats,"},{"time":1083000,"text":"and it is picked up"},{"time":1085000,"text":"by an autonomous airplane,"},{"time":1088000,"text":"and it's brought back to the laboratory"},{"time":1091000,"text":"within 24 hours of the eruption."},{"time":1093000,"text":"This is doable. All the pieces are there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1099000,"text":"A laboratory: many of you heard what happened"},{"time":1101000,"text":"on 9/7."},{"time":1103000,"text":"Some doctors in New York City removed"},{"time":1105000,"text":"the gallbladder of a woman in France."},{"time":1109000,"text":"We could do work on the sea floor that would be stunning,"},{"time":1111000,"text":"and it would be on live TV,"},{"time":1113000,"text":"if we have interesting things to show."},{"time":1116000,"text":"So we can bring an entirely new telepresence"},{"time":1119000,"text":"to the world, throughout the ocean."},{"time":1122000,"text":"This -- I've shown you sea floor --"},{"time":1124000,"text":"but so the goal here is real time interaction"},{"time":1126000,"text":"with the oceans from anywhere on earth."},{"time":1131000,"text":"It's going to be amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1134000,"text":"And as I go here,"},{"time":1136000,"text":"I just want to show you what we can bring into classrooms,"},{"time":1139000,"text":"and indeed, what we can bring into your pocket."},{"time":1145000,"text":"Many of you don't think of this yet,"},{"time":1147000,"text":"but the ocean will be in your pocket."},{"time":1149000,"text":"It won't be long. It won't be long."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153000,"text":"So let me leave you then"},{"time":1156000,"text":"with a few words"},{"time":1158000,"text":"from another poet, if you'll forgive me."},{"time":1164000,"text":"In 1943,"},{"time":1166000,"text":"T.S. Eliot wrote the \"Four Quartets.\""},{"time":1168000,"text":"He won the Nobel Prize for literature"},{"time":1170000,"text":"in 1948."},{"time":1173000,"text":"In \"Little Gidding\" he says --"},{"time":1175000,"text":"speaking I think for the human race,"},{"time":1177000,"text":"but certainly for the TED Conference and Sylvia --"},{"time":1181000,"text":"\"We shall not cease from exploration,"},{"time":1184000,"text":"and the end of all our exploring"},{"time":1186000,"text":"will be to arrive where we started"},{"time":1188000,"text":"and know the place for the first time,"},{"time":1191000,"text":"arrive through the unknown remembered gate"},{"time":1194000,"text":"where the last of earth left to discover"},{"time":1197000,"text":"is that which was the beginning."},{"time":1200000,"text":"At the source of the longest river"},{"time":1203000,"text":"the voice of a hidden waterfall"},{"time":1206000,"text":"not known because not looked for,"},{"time":1210000,"text":"but heard, half heard"},{"time":1214000,"text":"in the stillness beneath the waves of the sea.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1218000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1220000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}